---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About Us | Green Pendap Production"
    description="Meet the team behind Green Pendap Production."
>
    <div class="bg-gpp-primary/20 py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-4"
            >
                About Us
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Building dreams, one pixel at a time.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg mx-auto">
                <p class="lead text-2xl text-gpp-accent mb-8">
                    Green Pendap Production started with a simple idea: games
                    should be more than just entertainmentâ€”they should be
                    experiences that stick with you.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Founded in 2024, our studio brings together a diverse team
                    of artists, programmers, and storytellers who share a
                    passion for creating unique worlds. We believe in the power
                    of interactive storytelling and the joy of well-crafted
                    mechanics.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Our Philosophy
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We don't just make games; we craft experiences. Every pixel,
                    every line of dialogue, and every sound effect is carefully
                    considered to immerse player in our worlds. We value
                    creativity over trends and player experience over
                    monetization.
                </p>

                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold font-display text-white mt-12 mb-6"
                >
                    Join The Team
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We are always looking for talented individuals to join our
                    ranks. If you are passionate about game development and want
                    to work in an environment that values creativity and
                    work-life balance, check out our careers page or send us
                    your portfolio.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
